## SessionDelegate.onAckTimeout() method

Timeout waiting for ACK request. If no handler is provided the Session will terminated with a BYE. https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3261\#section-13.3.1.4

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
onAckTimeout?(): void;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`void`
